tip.text: Fantastic hotel with a view of Victoria Harbour. There is complimentary wifi, free minibar as well as a smartphone with complimentary international calls and 3G data.
Whilst you might have to wait in line for a short while, it will be well worth the wait!
The dan zai noodles are pretty amazing here (担仔面), and at NT$30, you can have a couple!
Great tasting food at affordable prices. This place is a must repeat visit for any foodie. Highlights include giant chicken schnitzels, grilled wagyu beef cubes and pancakes.
